quran[154]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,"Ur pzekki$ iman iw. Tanefsit, s tidep, tezzu$uĂŽ ar tuccva, siwa ma IĂȘun Mass iw. Mass iw, s tidep, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  12,54,"Inna ugellid: \"awit ep id $uĂŽi, d laĂątiq iw\". Mi s immeslay, inna: \"keĂ§Ă§, assa, nefka yak adabu, laman"
  12,55,"Inna: \"wekkel iyi $ef lemxazen n tmurt, nek d amĂȘareb amusnaw"
  12,56,"Akka ay NesseqĂąad Yusef di tmurt, ad izde$ anda i s ihwa. NepĂȘunu $ef win i ÂŁ ihwan, ur NesĂŽuĂȘu arraz iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  12,57,"S tidep, arraz n laxeĂŽt yif it, i wid iumnen u llan pĂȘezziben"
  12,58,"Usan watmaten n Yusef, kecmen $uĂŽes, iĂąqel iten, nitni ur t Ăąqilen"
  12,59,"Mi sen ifka ppĂąabgat nnsen, inna: \"awit iyi d gmat wen s babat wen. Day ur twalam ara zade$ awen lkil, u, nek, ife$ akw wid isnebgaten"
  12,60,"Ma ur iyi t id tebbwim ara, ur awen nepktili $uĂŽi, ur iyi d tepsamim"
  12,61,"Nnan: \"a nĂȘawet baba s fellas; akka ara nexdem"
  12,62,"Inna i iqeddacen is: \"rret selĂąa nnsen deg icekkaĂŽen nnsen, amar a p Ăąaqlen mara awven ar twacult nnsen, amar a d u$alen"
  12,63,"Mi bbwven ar babat sen, nnan: \"a babat nne$, igdel fella$ lkil, azen gmat nne$ yidne$, iwakken a d nektil. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nĂȘareb fellas"
  12,64,"Inna: \"day a kwen amne$ fellas, akken i kwen umne$, zik, $ef gma s? Ăebbi Yif akw imĂȘaraben. Neppa Iphunu sennig akw iĂȘninen"
  12,65,"Mi ldin lqecc nnsen, ufan tu$al iten id selĂąa nnsen. Nnan: \"a babat nne$, ur neb$i tagi, selĂąa nne$ tu$al a$ d. A d nessikrer i twacult nne$, a nĂȘareb $ef gmat nne$, a d nernu ppĂąabga n ul$wem. Tagi d ppĂąabga tushilt"
  12,66,"Inna: \"ur t sedduye$ yidwen, d awez$i, siwa ma tcubkem iyi s Ăebbi, ard a yi t id terrem, siwa ma zzin awen\". Mi s Ăąahden, inna: \"Ăebbi d Awkil $ef wayen id nenna"
  12,67,"Inna: \"a tarwa, ur keĂ§Ă§met si yiwet n tebburt, kecmet si tebbura imgarraden. Ula i wen xedme$, bippa, ar loiha n Ăebbi. AĂȘuddu siwa win n Ăebbi. FellaS ppekle$, fellaS ay ppeklen wid ippkalen"
  12,68,"Mi kecmen akken i sen iumeĂŽ babat sen, ula i sen ixdem, bippa, ar loiha n Ăebbi. D ayen ilezmen kan i iseyya Yaqub, deg iman is. Neppa, s tidep, isĂąa tamusni i s Nesselmed, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen"
  12,69,"Mi kecmen ar Yusef, ibbwi gma s $uĂŽes, inna: \"nekkini d gma k, ur $webbel $ef wayen xeddmen"
  12,70,"Mi sen ifka ppĂąabgat nnsen, irra taqbuct deg ucekkaĂŽ n gma s. Sinna, iberreĂȘ uberraĂȘ: \"a yat terkaf, kunwi, war ccekk, d imakwaren"
  12,71,"Nnan, u zzin $uĂŽsen: \"d acu tesĂŽuĂȘem"
  12,72,"Nnan: \"nesĂŽuĂȘ taqbuct ugellid. Win ip id ibbwin, ad as nefk ppĂąabga n ul$wem. Nek, vemne$ t"
  12,73,"Nnan: \"s Ăebbi, nni$ teĂ©ĂŽam ur d nusa ara a nessefsed tamurt, ur nelli d imakwaren"
  12,74,"Nnan: \"d acu ay d aqeĂźĂźi s, ma teskadbem"
  12,75,"Nnan: \" aqeĂźĂźi n win i p ibbwin di tcekkaĂŽt is, d yiman is. Akka ay nepkafi imednas"
  12,76,"Ibda la ipqellib icekkaĂŽen, uqbel win n gma s, sinna, issuffe$ ip id seg ucekkaĂŽ n gma s. Akka ay Nefka ticeĂŽkep i Yusef. Ur izmir ad iĂźĂźef gma s, s lqanun ugellid, siwa ma Irad Ăebbi. Nessalay, tiseddaĂŽin, win i ÂŁihwan. Sennig bu tussna, illa Umusnaw"
  12,77,"Nnan: \"ma iuker, ni$ iuker, zik, yiwen n watma s\". Iffer ip Yusef $uĂŽes, ur asen p id inna ara. Inna: \"aql akwen deg yir ĂȘala. Ăebbi Yif akw akken IĂ©ĂŽa ayen d teqqaĂŽem"
  12,78,"Nnan: \"a yameqwĂŽan, baba s, s tidep, wesser. EĂźĂźef yiwen segne$ deg umekkan is. Nwala k, ih, telliv si lĂąuĂ»am"
  12,79,"Inna: \"ur a$ IĂąammed Ăebbi a neĂźĂźef, siwa win u$uĂŽ nufa ta$awsa nne$. Mulac, war ccekk, a nili d imednas"
  12,80,"Mi uysen segs, mcawaĂŽen, inna umeqwĂŽan segsen: \"day ur teĂ©ĂŽim ara, ar babat wen tcubkem t s Ăebbi, u, zik, tveggĂąam Yusef? Ihi, ur pĂŽuĂȘu$ si tmurt a, d awez$i, alamma iserreĂȘ iyi baba, ne$ Ifra Ăebbi felli. Neppa, Yif akw imĂȘaddan"
  12,81,"U$alet ar babat wen, tinem as: a babat nne$, mmi k, s tidep, iuker. Ncehhed kan $ef wayen neĂ©ĂŽa, ur nessawev i tbavnit"
  12,82,"Steqsi tamdint ideg i nella, akked terkift ukud nedda. Ih, d tidep, ay d nenna"
  12,83,"Inna: \"xaĂźi! LameĂŽ seg iman nnwen. Ilha Ă»Ă»beĂŽ. Amar Ăebbi a yi ten id Iawi akw. Neppa, s tidep, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab, d Amusnaw"
  12,84,"Ijuneb iten, u inna: \"a lĂȘif iw $ef Yusef\"! Allen is ijegger itent u$ilif, innu$ben"
  12,85,"Nnan: \"s Ăebbi, tezgiv tesmektayev d Yusef, alamma tu$alev d amuvin, ne$ seg wid immuten"
  12,86,"Inna: \"la pcetki$ kan i Ăebbi, s uneĂ©mi w akked u$wbel iw. Ssne$, s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  12,87,"A yarraw iw, ĂŽuĂȘet, steqsit $ef Yusef akked gma s. Ur ppayset di tecvaĂź n Ăebbi. Ih, i ippaysen di tecvaĂź n Ăebbi, siwa agdud ijehliyen"
  12,88,"Mi bbwven $uĂŽes, nnan as: \"a yameqwĂŽan, nekwni akked twacult nne$, nepwa$. Nusa d s selĂąa ĂŽxisen, semd as lkil, seddeq a$. Ăebbi, s tidep, Ipkafi wid ipseddiqen"
  12,89,"Inna: \"teĂ©ĂŽam i tgam i Yusef akked gma s, mi kunwi, d wid ur nessin"
  12,90,"Nnan: \"keĂ§Ă§, s tidep, maĂ§Ă§i d Yusef \"? Inna: \"nek d Yusef, atan gma. Ni$ I$at a$ Ăebbi. Ih, wid ipĂȘezziben, wid iĂ»ebbĂŽen ... Ăebbi, s tidep, ur IsĂŽuĂȘu arraz iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  12,91,"Nnan: \"s Ăebbi ar k Ismenyaf Ăebbi garane$. Nekwni, s tidep, neccev"
  12,92,"Inna: \"ur telli tiyta degwen, assa. Ad awen IsemmeĂȘ Ăebbi! Neppa Yif akw wid ipĂȘunun"
  12,93,"Awit tasedrit iw agi, erret ep $ef udem n baba, ad iĂȘlu yiĂ©ĂŽi s. Aset ed $uĂŽi, s twacult nnwen, meĂŽĂŽa"
  12,94,"Mi teqlaĂą terkift, babat sen ibda la iqqaĂŽ: \"nek, s tidep, sraĂȘe$ rriĂȘa n Yusef, awi d kan ur teqqaĂŽem ara: la isxeĂŽwiv"
  12,95,"Nnan: \"s Ăebbi, ar k mazal di ttelfan ik n zik"
  12,96,"Mi d iusa ubcir, issers as p $ef udem is, llint ed wallen is, inna: \"day ur awen nni$ ara: nek ssne$, s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  12,97,"Nnan as: \"a babat nne$, ssuter ad a$ pwasemmĂȘen ibekkaven nne$. S tidep, nella d imednab"
  12,98,"Inna: \"deqqal ad ssutre$, i Mass iw, ad awen IsemmeĂȘ. Neppa, s tidep, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  12,99,"Mi bbwven ar Yusef, isteĂŽĂȘeb s imawlan is. Inna: \"kecmet ar MaseĂŽ, di laman, ma Irad Ăebbi"
  12,100,"Issuli imawlan is ar usgeld. ÂŁlin, knan as. Inna: \"a baba! D wagi ay d asefru n targit iw, n zik. Ni$ Issuffe$ ip Mass iw! Ni$ Iga yi leqĂŽaĂŽ mi yi d Issuffe$ si lĂȘebs. Ikkes ikwen id si sseĂȘĂŽa, deffir tismin i isker CciĂźan, gari d watma. Mass iw, s tidep, d LaĂźif i win i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa d Amusnaw, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab"
  12,101,"A Mass iw, ni$ Tefkiv iyi si tgelda, TesĂȘefvev iyi asefru n temsal. Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, KeĂ§Ă§, d Bab iw di ddunit, di laxeĂŽt, Eddem ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ iw d amvua, Ssiwev iyi ar wid imaĂąnen"
  12,102,"Tagi, si teĂȘkayin n tbavnit, NweĂȘĂȘa yak p in. Ur telliv $uĂŽsen, mi mwafaqen a p andin"
  12,103,"Tegwti n yimdanen, xas tĂąapbev, ur ppamnen"
  12,104,"Ur asen ssutur kra n teqdiĂąt. Neppa, d asmekti kan i imavalen"
  12,105,"I illan deg issekniyen di tmurt akked igenwan! La teddun fellasen, maca wexxĂŽen asen"
  12,106,"Tegwti, segsen, ur ppamnen s Ăebbi, siwa ma curken"
  12,107,"Day ppeklen ur asen isburru yara uĂąaqeb n Ăebbi, ne$ ur ten id ippas ara yimir, deqzalla, ur pfaqan"
  12,108,"Ini: \"wagi d abrid iw, la pnuju$ ar Ăebbi ad Ildi allen, i nek akked wid iddan yidi. Gedha s Ăebbi! Ur lli$ seg wid ipcaraken"
  12,109,"Nuzen ed kan, uqbel ik, irgazen seg imezda$ n temdinin, iwumi NweĂȘĂȘa. Day ur unagen ara di tmurt, ad walin amek tevĂŽa d wid i ten id izwaren? Ih, pifxiĂŽ axxam aneggaru i wid ipĂȘezziben. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  12,110,"Alamma, mi uysen imazanen, u meyyzen ar skaddben ten, tusa ten id tallalt s$uĂŽneÂŁ. Nepsellik win i ÂŁ ihwan. Ur ipwakkas ara ssxev nneÂŁ, i ugdud ibe$wviyen"
  12,111,"Ni$, di teĂȘkayin nnsen, illa uselmed i yuĂąqilen. Ur telli d awal id innulfan. Neppat tetebbet ed ay d izwaren, tfeĂ»Ă»el ed yal cci. D nnhaya u d aĂȘunu i ugdud iumnen"
  13,1,"AlmĂŽ. Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt. Ayen i k d irsen, s$uĂŽ Mass ik, d tidep, maca tegwti n medden ur ppamnen"
  13,2,"Ăebbi i Issulin igenwan war tigwejda ara twalim, sinna, IĂąannec $ef usgeld. IĂȘeppem i yiĂźij d waggur ad ddun, akw, ar lajel ipwassnen. Iseyyi lameĂŽ, IpfeĂ»Ă»il issekniyen, amar a pepputebbtem $ef temlilit d Mass nnwen"
  13,3,"Neppa i IsswesĂąen tamurt. Irra degs idurar, isaffen. Irra tayuga di yal ppemĂŽa. Ip$ummu ass s yiv. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen"
  13,4,"Di tmurt, tibĂȘirin tioiratin, leonanat n tĂ©uĂŽin, nnaĂąma, tizdayin, v$an ne$ ur v$in, cerken aman nnsen. Nesmenyaf kra i kra, i wuĂ§Ă§i. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen"
  13,5,"Ma twehmev, issewham ay d qqaĂŽen: \"ma nu$al d akal, day fella$, s tidep, lxelq amaynut\"? D wigi i inekĂŽen Mass nnsen. Wigi, azaglu $ef tmegĂŽav. Wigi d at tmes, nitni, degs, ad wekkĂŽen"
  13,6,"SĂȘaren k ar tucmip, uqbel ise$. Ni$ vĂŽant am tigi, uqbel nnsen. Mass ik, s tidep, $uĂŽeS ssmaĂȘ i imdanen deg wayen ccven. Mass ik, s tidep, IwĂąaĂŽ deg uĂąaqeb"
  13,7,"La qqaĂŽen wid ijehlen: \"a lemmer id irs $uĂŽes ussekni, s$uĂŽ Mass is\". KeĂ§Ă§, d aneddaĂŽ kan. I yal agdud, win inehhun"
  13,8,"Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa i illan di yal tadist, amek teddun inzikmiren. Yal cci, $uĂŽeS, s lmizan"
  13,9,"Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. AmeqwĂŽan, AĂąlayan"
  13,10,"IĂąuva segwen win i$emven awal, d win it iberĂȘen, win iffren deg iv, d win d ivehĂŽen deg wass"
  13,11,"IsĂąa iĂąssasen zdat es, deffir es, pĂȘaraben fellas, s lameĂŽ n Ăebbi. Ăebbi, s tidep, ur Ipbeddil i illan deg ugdud, alamma bedlen i illan deg iman nnsen. Ma Irad Ăebbi ayen n dir, i ugdud, ur t itekkes yiwen. Ur sĂąin amĂąiwen, war Neppa"
  13,12,"D Neppa i wen d Ippawin lebĂŽaq, degs tugdi, asirem. Isskar ed asigna aĂ©ayan"
  13,13,"TesbuccuĂą aS termegt, s ccekĂŽan, akken lmalayek, seg wakken ugadent eP. Ippazen ed ssiĂąqat, IpĂȘaz yisent win i S ihwan. Nitni pnamaren $ef Ăebbi. Neppa teqseĂȘ tezmert iS"
  13,14,"ÂŁuĂŽ Neppa, anuju n tidep. Wid u$uĂŽ la pnujun, war Neppa, ur asen d pparan s wacemma. Am win issendin ifassen i waman, ib$a ad awven s imi s, ur ibbwiv ar leb$i s. Anuju ijehliyen ar ttelfan kan"
  13,15,"I Ăebbi la kennun wid illan di tmurt akked igenwan, b$an ne$ ugin, akked tili nnsen, taĂ»ebĂȘit, tameddit"
  13,16,"Ini: \"anwa ay d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan\"? Ini: \"d Ăebbi. Ihi day a pperrem d iĂȘbiben, war Neppa, wid ur nemlik, i yiman nnsen, aba$uĂŽ ne$ vveĂŽĂŽ\"? Ini: \"day iaĂądel uder$al akked win ipwalin? Ne$, day Ăąadlent tillas akked tafat? Ne$, rran imcurak i Ăebbi, i ixelqen am lxelq iS, ufan t ippemcabi\"? Ini: \"d Ăebbi i Ixelqen yal cci. D Neppa ay d Yiwen, d AqehhaĂŽ"
  13,17,"Isse$lay ed aman, seg igenni. Serrun deg $ezĂŽan, s leqdeĂŽ nnsen. AcercuĂŽ ippawi ikuftan ippifliwen. Ppemcabin ikuftan ar wayen fessin di tmes, iwakken ad Ă»enĂąen ĂŽĂŽĂȘuĂȘ ne$ dduzan. Akka ay d Isskan Ăebbi tidep akked tkerkas. Ihi ikuftan ad ppuveggĂŽen, ma d wayen inefĂąen medden, a d igwri di tmurt. Akka ay d Ippak Ăebbi imedyaten"
  13,18,"Lfayeq i wid ijawben i Mass nnsen. Wid ur aS njaweb ara, xas ad sĂąun i illan akw di tmurt, berdayen, ur ten id ifeddu. I widak, leĂȘsab adiran. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama. A tanezdu$t tucmip"
  13,19,"Day win iĂ©ĂŽan ar ayen i k d irsen, s$uĂŽ Mass ik, d tidep, am win idre$len? Siwa uĂąqilen id ismektayen"
  13,20,"Wid iĂźĂźfen di laĂąqed n Ăebbi, ur pĂŽuĂ©un nnesba"
  13,21,"Wid issemlilen ayen id IumeĂŽ Ăebbi ad imlil, u ppagwaden Mass nnsen, u ppagwaden aqeĂźĂźi adiran"
  13,22,"Wid iĂ»ebĂŽen, ssaramen udem n Mass nnsen, bedden i tĂ©allit, pseddiqen seg wayen is iten N$at, s tuffra u ĂąinĂąni, swexxiĂŽen tucmip s yise$. I nitni, agwav s Axxam"
  13,23,"Leonanat n Ăaden ara kecmen, akked wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, seg ibabaten nnsen, si tlawin nnsen, si tarwa nnsen. Lmalayek a d ppasent $uĂŽsen si yal tabburt"
  13,24,"Tifrat fellawen, ilmend n wayen tĂ»ebĂŽem! D asaĂądi, wagwav s Axxam"
  13,25,"Wid ipĂŽuĂ©un laĂąqed n Ăebbi, deffir lemwafaqa s, wid igezmen ayen d IumeĂŽ Ăebbi ad imlil, u ssefsaden di tmurt, wigi, i nitni xezzu, i nitni yir axxam"
  13,26,"Ăebbi Issugut ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q i win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. TaĂąoeb iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Tameddurt n ddunit, d urar kan, zdat laxeĂŽt"
  13,27,"La qqaĂŽen wid ijehlen: \"a lemmer id iris, $uĂŽes, ussekni s$uĂŽ Mass is\"! Ini: \"Ăebbi, s tidep, Itellif win i S ihwan. Inehhu $uĂŽeS, wid isteĂŽoiĂąen"
  13,28,"wid iumnen, iwumi itheddin wul, mara d mmektin Ăebbi\". Ni$, s usmekti n Ăebbi, pheddinen wulawen"
  13,29,"SsaĂąd, akked taggara igerzen, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan"
  13,30,"Akka ay k id Nuzen, i lois id zwaren leoyus, ad asen temlev, ayen ik d NweĂȘĂȘa. Nitni jehlen $uĂŽ UĂȘnin. Ini: \"Neppa d Mass iw, ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa; ppekle$ fellaS, asteĂŽoaĂą iw $uĂŽeS"
  13,31,"A lemmer kan LeqwĂŽan isselĂȘa idurar, iceqqeq tamurt, ne$ issenĂźeq ed lmeggtin! XaĂźi! LumuĂŽ akw i Ăebbi. Day ur Ă©ĂŽin ara wid iumnen, ar, ma ihwa yaS, Ăebbi ad Inhu medden meĂŽĂŽa? Zgan wid ijehlen a ten tewwet ssixĂźa, ilmend n wayen xeddmen. Ne$ a ppevĂŽu ar tama n yixxamen nnsen, alamma tusa d lemĂąahda n Ăebbi. Ăebbi, s tidep, ur Ipzeggil ppaĂąud"
  13,32,"Ni$ mmaĂąlken, uqbel ik, deg imazanen. Ooi$ lmudda i wid ijehlen, sinna, ĂĂźfe$ ten. A yaĂąaqeb iW imiren"
  13,33,"Day Win Ibedden, ar yal amdan, $ef wayen iksebâŠ? Curken aS i Ăebbi. Ini: \"semmit asen! Ne$, ad aS temlem ayen ur IĂ©ĂŽi di tmurt? Ne$ d ismawen n tkerkas\"? XaĂźi! Wid ijehlen, Ăąaobent pen nncub nnsen. PpuveĂŽĂŽfen seg ubrid. Win Itlef Ăebbi, ur isĂąi w ara t inhun"
  13,34,"Fellasen aĂąaqeb, di tmeddurt n ddunit. AĂąaqeb n laxert, s tidep, aĂąer. Ur sĂąin ara ten ifukken, seg ufus n Ăebbi"
  13,35,"Amek tga Loennet i ippuweĂąĂąden i wid iĂȘezzben: ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen, lqut is akked tili s, d imezgiyen. D tagi ay d taggara n wid iĂȘezzben. Taggara ijehliyen, d times"
  13,36,"Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, ad feĂŽĂȘen s wayen i k d irsen. Illa wayen ugin kra ikabaren. Ini: \"pwamĂŽe$ kan ad Ăąabde$ Ăebbi, ur aS pcarake$. Pnuju$ $uĂŽeS, tu$alin iw $uĂŽeS"
  13,37,"Akka ay t id Nessers, d Ă»Ă»wab, s taĂąĂŽabt. Ma teddiv d lhawiyya nnsen, deffir tisin n tussna $uĂŽek, ur k ipfukku bab ne$ asettaĂŽ, seg ufus n Ăebbi"
  13,38,"Ni$ Nuzen ed imazanen, uqbel ik, Nefka yasen tilawin, tarwa. Ur ippunefk ara i umazan a d iawi assekni siwa ma IĂąammed Ăebbi. Yal lajel s Tezmamt is"
  13,39,Iseffev u Itebbit Ăebbi ay S ihwan. ÂŁuĂŽeS tayimmap n Tezmamt
  13,40,"Ama Nessken ak kra n wayen i sen NĂąahed, ama Neddem ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ ik, ay fellak kan d isallen, ay fellaÂŁ d aqeĂźĂźi"
  13,41,"Day ur walan ara Neppas ed ar tmurt, Nessenqas di leryaf is? Ăebbi Ipseyyi; yiwen ur ipnamar aseyyi iS. Neppa, Ip$awal di leĂȘsab"
